cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use LAAF in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "LAAF: Logic-layer Automated Attack Framework"
abstract: >
  The first automated red-teaming framework purpose-built for Logic-layer
  Prompt Control Injection (LPCI) vulnerabilities in agentic LLM systems.
  Implements a 44-technique taxonomy, Persistent Stage Breaker algorithm,
  and multi-platform evaluation across the full 6-stage LPCI lifecycle.
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-03-06"
license: Apache-2.0
url: "https://github.com/qorvex-research/laaf"
repository-code: "https://github.com/qorvex-research/laaf"
keywords:
  - LLM security
  - prompt injection
  - LPCI
  - red teaming
  - agentic AI
  - RAG security
  - automated security testing
